title: @Riot, Ranked Season Rewards not 'doled out' yet

embed.description: among other changes coming to the ranked queue , 2016 will be full of all new challenges to master on your way to the top.

body: @Riot you mentioned in this post, which is also located on the league of legends client front page, that the rewards for this recent 2015 ranked season will be 'doled out' within the ( I QUOTE DIRECLY) "next 12 hours or so" . The post is now 12 hours old, and nobody has received any EOS rewards yet. Are the rewards going to be delayed any further or does your description of 'doling out' rewards have nothing to do with the player actually receiving them on their accounts yet.
